    "body": "@kamami \r\nFYI, I have downgraded Algoliasearch to version 4.24.0, and it's now working. The problem seems to be with version 5 of Algoliasearch. That said, this does not resolve the underlying issues, but it is a workaround to avoid the error.\r\n\r\nI have also changed this => `import { liteClient as algoliasearch } from algoliasearch/lite;` \r\nBy this => `import algoliasearch from algoliasearch/lite;`",
